{"tid":1282076,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG+WS]組團玩Boardgame TRPG同LARP(重post)","createTime":"2019-07-03T13:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T06:19:52.000Z","uid":85363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce001819f6740b2618a3f922954f3278a2e370f","tid":1282076,"uid":85363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:02:41.000Z","msg":"我們以推廣TRPG及LARP為目標，希望可以提供一個平台給有興趣進入Role-playing世界的玩家享受扮演的樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n現時我們正主力推廣LARP，LARP的全稱為Live Action Role Playing，即實時動作角色扮演。LARP是角色扮演遊戲的其中一種，玩家在扮演角色的同時需要做出相應的動作，與其他角色互動。<br />\n<br />\n歐美地區的LARP活動大多是以龍與地下城作背景的cosplay冒險遊戲。在華語地區，LARP則以推理調查犯罪案件為主。玩家會收到各自選取的角色劇本，在遊戲中透過與其他角色互動交流，加上調查各種各樣的線索，嘗試還原故事真相以及演活你所選擇的角色。當然最重要的還是享受身為舞台劇一員的樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n日後亦會不定時推出TRPG團(包括COC或DND系統)給各位參加。<br />\n<br />\n如有興趣加入，可參與以下Telegram組團群組或Whatsapp群組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/fluffyballtheatre\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffluffyballtheatre&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHife5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=d0608c45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fluffyballtheatre</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/DjmXHFXw6ZjBjBOsM3gFV6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchat.whatsapp.com%2FDjmXHFXw6ZjBjBOsM3gFV6&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHife5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=ddb90975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chat.whatsapp.com/DjmXHFXw6ZjBjBOsM3gFV6</a>"},{"pid":"53663cad531311b6d221b30b40d454b5a6874893","tid":1282076,"uid":85363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"我地每個月都會推出活動供群組成員報名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ffc0ab5b7ac6938563f09f87a5acc6a73200c1","tid":1282076,"uid":85363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:19:52.000Z","msg":"推推POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}